cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper is about multi-object tracking (MOT) system, which involves computer vision and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves motion modeling and adaptive appearance feature fusion, which are related to robotics and artificial intelligence, respectively. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. The paper also presents a state-of-the-art accuracy on MOT16&17 challenges, which involves evaluating the performance of the system. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.MM (Multimedia) are also possible categories.
